                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.5 <gloss target="#t_MAP1"
                    >MAP</gloss>/1–2750</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by the <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-01-27">January 27,
                            1950</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have today approved, as satisfying the pertinent provisions of the Mutual
                    Defense Assistance Act of 1949, the recommendations for the integrated defense
                    of the North Atlantic area made by the North Atlantic Council and Defense
                    Committee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harry Truman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
